Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:04.80,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Encounters are mysterious!\NBut the world is even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.93,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:10.34,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today is a serious code!\NIf adding doesn't work, try subtracting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:11.91,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.77,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:16.30,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:43.01,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Kaori, the daughter of the novelist Nintaro Shinmei,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:48.12,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}asked the old guy to find her parents who went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:51.32,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}They've been missing for two months,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:55.88,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}but the publisher still receives his manuscripts for his new series.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.55,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We went straight to the publishing company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:06.27,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We found several incomprehensible things about his manuscripts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.87,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and they turned out to be a code calling for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:19.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There's a message from Shinmei-{\i1}sensei{\i0} hidden in these lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:25.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Which makes it all fit:\Nthat provocative dedication,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:30.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}the author's appearance in the story,\Nand the odd lines of dialogue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:37.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But what is the goal of the person holding him and his wife captive?!
